ze:18px;\">Don't wait to hear your vet say \"$6,000, no guarantees.\"</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">Don't wait to make the choice that will haunt you forever.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">Because now you know.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOkJgAH-s-_label","label":"ggOkJgAH-s-_label","default":"<p>Apply Discount &amp; Check Availability</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7zAnQhlOf_text","label":"gg7zAnQhlOf_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\"><i>Click the link above to see if Waggier is still offering a 33% discount and free shipping</i></span></p>"}],
